reviewText: now I have the whole collection this season 5 I have to play on my laptop cause of the different region. but do not care. I have them all.
I love this series -  all 5 seasons.  It's fun, with great characters.  Just wish there were more seasons!

The end of a very good series of stories about the Dracula family in England. The Count, Vlad and Ingrid all finish off their adventures in style. I thought the ending rather good, although I will not spoil it for any who wish to explore this series. Warning, this is a PAL disc, so you will need a multi-region DVD player, it will not play on a regular DVD player!
Good show just wish amazon had season 5 for down load
Please release this last season on DVD for all regions - (or at least for USA).  I would like to see this last season as I'm hooked on the previous seasons.
